title: Kitchen Witch - 2015 - Trouble
description:
If John Lee Hooker, Kyuss and Janis Joplin had a baby, can you imagine how ugly that little alcoholic baby would be? Fortunately Kitchen Witch can hold their liquor long enough to write some booty shakin' blues-based stoner grooves. Check out the tunes and see if they can put a spell on you too!

This is their first EP, Trouble.
